schema:name: 43 This is a fish counting bucket about to be lowered into the holding tank for collecting and counting. After the fish are allowed to collect in the holding tank for 10 minutes a count is made. This figure is multiplied by 12 to determine the number of fish collected over a two hour period, at which time another count is made. This is a continuous twenty-four hour a day count on every odd hour.
